{"title":"纤夫谣","authors":["孙新凯"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤夫谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙新凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水弯弯，路弯弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空抛下一条缆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤夫踩着云雾走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤着河呀拉着山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿哟嘿——人在唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿哟嘿——山在喘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是蜀道胜蜀道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步攀登步步难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百里拉纤象抬轿——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缆在抖，船在颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢慢纤过道道水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓抬起重重山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉纤号子象神话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年编，代代传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神仙帮咱搓缆绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮帮咱来拉船……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩拉纤绳望明月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口喊号子心在盼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松籽盼成撑天林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头踩成河卵蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红，太阳升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舞，乌云散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大祖国向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱要插翅把纤换……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了“四害”来了妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航道扣上铁锁链；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩拉纤绳步难抬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光喊号子不大干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤夫想飞飞不得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步盼，行路难……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼到十月金风起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷云吐雾一溜烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻飞过道道水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠飘上重重山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老纤夫，船头坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟锅上面星儿闪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪象云朵云象浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天在船底船在天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月不纤船船纤月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船工就象活神仙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年神话传到今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传到今天不新鲜……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}